      },
      "date": "2013-06-27 15:54:12.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: I would prefer that you didn't submit this\n\n(4 inline comments)\n\nSee comments - there is room for improvement here, as well as one particular problem that could lead to more silent failures.  \n\nI'm also almost inclined to say we should instead fix the test case to not pass multiple directories to test_mkdir, and also fix test_mkdir to fail if more than one directory is passed.  That would make the error handing in the test case more explicit, but perhaps we don't need to go that far.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 1
    },
